      <h1 class="blog-title">Worcester Bosch vs Vaillant: Which Is the Best Boiler for Liverpool Homes in 2026?</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">The two most popular premium boiler brands assessed head to head for Liverpool properties. Efficiency, warranty, reliability and real installed prices all compared by our Gas Safe engineers.</p>
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <span><strong>By</strong> Ideal Plumbing Solutions</span>
        <span><strong>Gas Safe Registered Engineers</strong></span>
        <span>January 2026</span>
        <span>7 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div>
